###################################
### FreeCAD install with flatpak to get the latest version 
###################################

  Flatpak is the latest package/application distribution for Linux it allows the application to be packages
 just once and then be able to be installed on many of the Linux distros ( RedHad, Ubuntu, Debian, Raspberry OS...)
 It has made application packaging more standard and handles pre-reqs smoothly.

### Install flatpak
 sudo apt update
 sudo apt install -y flatpak
 sudo flatpak remote-add --if-not-exists flathub https://flathub.org/repo/flathub.flatpakrepo

### FreeCad and other useful MAKER Apps
 sudo flatpak install -y --system flathub org.freecad.FreeCAD  ### CAD/CAM 2D 3D
 sudo flatpak install -y flathub org.gimp.GIMP                 ### GNU Image Manipulation
 sudo flatpak install -y flathub org.inkscape.Inkscape         ### Inkscape

### flatpack management

### List installed flatpaks
 flatpak list

### List all available applications
 flatpak remote-ls flathub --app

### Update just flatpaks
 flatpak update


